## вңЁ Installation

Install the gem and add to the application's Gemfile by executing:

```console
bundle add {KJ|GEM_NAME}
```

If bundler is not being used to manage dependencies, install the gem by executing:

```console
gem install {KJ|GEM_NAME}
```

